@acton393 Does iOS support the `word-break` style now?
@misakuo It seem like iOS doesn't support `word-break`. I can support this later.
great work
please provide one or more testcase on  http://dotwe.org/vue

Thanks for your contribution, but all documents of Weex are moved to https://github.com/apache/incubator-weex-site now, and this link is [removed in the new documents](https://github.com/apache/incubator-weex-site/blob/f42e30d80cfb4b29d88cece64c63f148660faf26/source/guide/advanced/use-vuex-and-vue-router.md).

Hey ~ @misakuo @gubaojian 
This is a testcase -- [Word-Break](http://dotwe.org/vue/f5011e3908f4f4ab3b854bc5b990b880).
I found iOS doesn't support `word-break` style, but the default way is `break-all`.
I will create a new pull request later, then try to support it.
Thx you both.
